reviewText: Brian Free and Assurance does a wonderful job on this video.  Each of the guys give their testimonies - and each one is a blessing!  Many of their best songs are on this video.  I watch it over and over and over again!
Brian Free and Assurance Live.  Singing Southern Gospel.  Don't get no better!  Ivan Parker and Mike Lefevre helping out.  Midnight Cry is included also!!!
